item.title: Cleaning the Metropolitan Museum of Art
item.description: Recently, The Metropolitan Museum of Art made its collection database publicly available. The collection spans over 5,000 years and has nearly a half-million records. Wonderful! Exciting! 43 Variables, almost all of them text.
